host_about:
@BANGTEL loves designing and curating magical spaces for our guests! 

TimeOut Chicago named us the Best Bachelorette stay for 2020.  

Everything we do, is done with YOU, our guest, in mind!

We have stayed in so many wonderful AirBnBs around the world, we thought we would join the community. Local knowledge makes such a difference when you're traveling. We look forward to greeting you and pointing you in the right direction for your visit. Favorite mottos;
                            "Work hard. Play hard. Make a difference."
                                "Choose what you want, and pay for it."

